# Graph Pipeline Rule

Imperative `KycGraph` — NOT compiled LangGraph StateGraph (ADR-001).

## Node order (`src/graph/graph.ts`)
ingest → apiLookup → [browserFallback?] → draftDossier → guardrail

## Routing (`src/graph/edges.ts`)
- `afterApiLookup`: skip browser if `completeness === "complete" && uboVerified`
- guardrail sets `pending_hitl` or `completed` — HITL is external (ADR-002)

## Constraints
- Zod schemas in `src/graph/schemas.ts` — all LLM outputs validated (ADR-007)
- Per-node timeouts via `withTimeout()` in `graph.ts`
- State merge via `mergeState()` — evidence ledger is shallow-merged
- HITL: `POST /cases/:id/approve` — never auto-approve (INV-007)

## On change
Run `docs/instructions/IS-002-graph-node-change.md`
